# Provider Module

## Overview

Unified Provider Layer consolidates AI communication from auto-code-rs into provider/ module with SSE streaming

## Goals

- **G1** — Unified Provider Layer consolidates AI communication from auto-code-rs into provider/ module with SSE streaming

## Key Architecture Decisions

- **A1** — Unified Provider & Runtime Architecture

## Key Designs

- **D1** — Multi-Provider AI Dispatch
- **D2** — Unified Provider Layer

## Module Dependencies

Depends on: [agent-config](agent-config/module.ad), [api-sources](api-sources/module.ad), [cli](cli/module.ad), [runtime](runtime/module.ad)

